version_description:
Howdy farmers!

15 NEW LEVELS are here to cool you down this summer! Are your fingers ready for Winter Adventure?

Be sure to update Farm Heroes Super Saga for all the new content!

Good luck!

Are you ready to go off piste?

Play our new episode Ski Resort, and you'll be greeted with 15 NEW LEVELS. They're ice cold, so be sure to wrap up warm when you match those Cropsies!

Update to the latest version for all the new content. It's Farmtastic!

Hey farmers!

No need to wait any longer! We have 15 BRAND NEW LEVELS that will make you nuts! Can you spot the red squirrel?

Don’t forget to update to the latest version of the game to be able to see him!

CROPTASTIC news, farmers!

Didn’t have time to go on holidays during the summer? No problem! Pack your stuff and come with us to New England, with these 15 NEW LEVELS!

Remember to update to the latest version before closing your suitcase!

BOO!

Halloween is almost here, and we have some treats for you!
Pass the Fox Forest and reach the Pumpkin Farm to be ready for the spookiest night of the year!

Double the fun with these 30 NEW LEVELS!

Be sure to update to the latest version of the game to play them all!

Happy Halloween, farmers!

Maybe we don’t give you treats, but we can definitely gift you 15 NEW LEVELS! Each one served fresh from the Pumpkin Cart!

Don’t forget to update to the latest version of the game to celebrate Halloween in style!

Howdy, farmers!

Feeling the autumn blues? Worry no more!
We have 30, and I repeat, 30 NEW CROPTASTIC LEVELS for you to play!

Be sure to update to the latest version of the game!

Yippee-Ki-Yay ya got 45 NEW LEVELS to play! All the way from Campsite to Green Cabin to the end of Forest Oven - new SUPER adventures are waitin’ for yer farmtastic touch! Come ‘n’ play NOW!

Be sure to update to the latest version of the game!

Howdy, farmers!

Have ya ever wondered of playing Farm Heroes Super Saga in a tranquil Water Cabin? Yes?
Well, now you can! 15 NEW LEVELS are here to sharpen your switchin’ and matchin’ abilities!

Have you updated to the latest version of the game yet?

Hey, Partner!

Can you see that? It seems there is a mill in the woods! Let’s find out with these 15 NEW LEVELS! Don’t miss the chance to sharpen your matchin’ skills!

Don’t forget to update to the latest version of the game!

Farmtastic news, farmers!

We have 15 BRAND NEW LEVELS hidden within the Birch Land! Can you beat Rancid and pass them all in one week?

If you really want to be a master don’t forget to update to the latest version of the game!

Farmtastic news, farmers!

We have 15 BRAND NEW LEVELS hidden within the Birch Land! Can you beat Rancid and pass them all in one week?

If you really want to be a master don’t forget to update to the latest version of the game!

In need of a relaxing retreat, partner?

Head to the Forest Shack for some extreme switchin’ and matchin’ NOW! But be careful! This is also the Bear Retreat...GROWL!!!

If you want to enjoy 30 NEW LEVELS don’t forget to update to the latest version of the game!

Ahoy, farmers! Mayans once predicted it, didn’t you hear? 15 BRAND NEW LEVELS coming your way!

Yes, it’s true, it was on their list. Remember to update to the latest version of the game!

Who is hiding behind the trees?!?

If you want to find out make sure to update to the latest version of the game to get 15 BRAND NEW LEVELS!

Don’t miss out this farmtastic Mountain Tale!

Croptastic news, farmers!

If you were looking for a bit of a workout, don’t miss out on this amazing hike up to the Father Cabin! 15 NEW LEVELS are waiting for your fingers!

Don’t forget to update to the latest version of the game!

Howdy, farmers!

Spring is in the air, so why not jump into the Eastern Forest to sharpen those matchin’ skills of yours? We have 15 BRAND NEW LEVELS for you!

Don’t let that Rancid win, update to the latest version of the game!

Watch out, farmers!

Our journey continues with 15 BRAND NEW LEVELS, but be careful! Passing through the Wicked House won’t be easy!

Remember to make sure to update to the latest version of the game!

Howdy, farmers!

Merry Hamlet is here with 15 BRAND NEW LEVELS! Are you up to the challenge? Switch and match you way up to the top!

Remember to update to the latest version of the game!

Ahoy, farmers! Mayans once predicted it, didn’t you hear? 15 BRAND NEW LEVELS coming your way!

Yes, it’s true, it was on their list. Remember to update to the latest version of the game!

Think you can take on me?!

Pfft, as if! These 15 NEW LEVELS will have you shaking like washing machine on a spin cycle. Game on humans, game on!

Rancid the Raccoon
